jadacz.lib
Class Packet

java.lang.Object
  jadacz.lib.Packet

public class Packet
extends Object

Packet is a class used to transfer any data between clients and server. Every kind of data should be serialized to Packet before sending.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Szymon 'tecku' Kordyaczny
